          <ul>
            <li>Open the Sportsurge website</li>
            <li>Select your preferred sports league</li>
            <li>Choose a live match</li>
            <li>Click a working stream link and enjoy</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Popular Sports Available on Sportsurge</h2>

